== 音樂風格與形象 ==
Red Velvet的音樂風格分為「[[紅色|Red]]」以及「[[天鵝絨|Velvet]]」，「Red」展現強烈、活力的形象，而「Velvet」象徵成熟和優雅。近年，部分Red Velvet的作品將兩種風格混合在一起，以展現其豐富且多樣的音樂世界<ref>{{cite web|url=http://enter.etoday.co.kr/view/news_view.php?varAtcId=129349#cb|title=트와이스와 레드벨벳이 가는 길|date=2017-12-09|publisher=etoday|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527090830/https://was.livere.me/comment/etoday?id=etoday&refer=enter.etoday.co.kr%2Fview%2Fnews_view.php%3FvarAtcId%3D129349&uid=ODcwLzIyMDk0LzMyMDM%3D&site=http%3A%2F%2Fenter.etoday.co.kr%2Fview%2Fnews_view.php%3FvarAtcId%3D129349&title=%25255BBZ%2525uC2DC%2525uC120%25255D%252520%2525uD2B8%2525uC640%2525uC774%2525uC2A4%2525uC640%252520%2525uB808%2525uB4DC%2525uBCA8%2525uBCB3%2525uC774%252520%2525uAC00%2525uB294%252520%2525uAE38&titleLength=23&logo=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.etoday.co.kr%2Fpto_db%2F2017%2F12%2F20171207050801_1161707_600_400.jpg&uuid=b9ef9503-7c82-43c7-bf8b-32b46b92ba92#cb}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.star2.com/entertainment/music/music-reviews/2016/03/24/review-the-velvet-by-red-velvet/|title=Review: The Velvet by Red Velvet|date=2016-03-24|publisher=STAR2|archive-date=2018-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831002431/https://www.star2.com/entertainment/music/music-reviews/2016/03/24/review-the-velvet-by-red-velvet/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fuse.tv/2016/03/red-velvet-one-of-these-nights-mv|title=RED VELVET RETURNS WITH DREAMY R&B BALLAD 'ONE OF THESE NIGHTS': WATCH|date=2016-03-16|publisher=Fuse|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321071954/https://www.fuse.tv/2016/03/red-velvet-one-of-these-nights-mv}}</ref>。就[[音樂類型|音樂類型]]而言，「Red」的歌曲以[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行樂]]為主，例如《[[Dumb_Dumb|Dumb Dumb]]》、《[[Rookie_(Red_Velvet歌曲)|Rookie]]》、《[[紅色味道|紅色味道]]》等；「Velvet」的歌曲則以[[節奏藍調|R&B]]和[[抒情歌曲|抒情]]為主，例如《[[The_Velvet|One Of These Nights]]》、《[[Perfect_Velvet|Bad Boy]]》、《[[Psycho_(Red_Velvet歌曲)|Psycho]]》等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://popcrush.com/red-velvet-one-of-these-nights-the-velvet-mini-album/|title=Red Velvet Show Their Softer Side with ‘One Of These Nights'|date=2016-03-16|publisher=PopCrush}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iol.co.za/capeargus/life/watch-the-sa-starter-guide-to-k-pop-music-bts-red-velvet-exo-and-more-16410219|title=WATCH: The SA starter guide to K-pop music - BTS, Red Velvet, EXO and more|date=2018-09-06|publisher=Independent Online|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321071958/https://www.iol.co.za/capeargus/life/watch-the-sa-starter-guide-to-k-pop-music-bts-red-velvet-exo-and-more-16410219}}</ref>。另外，Red Velvet的雙重概念也影響著成員的造型，在「Red」的概念中會穿著色彩鮮豔的服裝，例如《[[Dumb_Dumb|Dumb Dumb]]》的紅衣娃娃和《[[The_ReVe_Festival:_Day_1|Zimzalabim]]》的螢光怪誕風格<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.yibada.com/articles/61568/20150908/red-velvet-are-sweet-creepy-dolls-in-dumb-dumb-mv-watch.htm|title=Red Velvet are Sweet-Creepy Dolls in “Dumb, Dumb” MV [Watch]|date=2015-09-08|publisher=YIBADA|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329222612/http://en.yibada.com/articles/61568/20150908/red-velvet-are-sweet-creepy-dolls-in-dumb-dumb-mv-watch.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/877680|title=Red Velvet穿上打歌服傻眼　「這褲子是出了什麼事」|date=2017-03-04|publisher=ETtoday|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809163432/http://star.ettoday.net/news/877680}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/red-velvet-fashion-transformation|title=See Red Velvet's Style Evolution From “Feel My Rhythm” to Debut|date=2022-03-24|publisher=teenVogue|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2022-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220429075807/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/red-velvet-fashion-transformation}}</ref>；而「Velvet」的概念中會穿著成熟的服裝，例如《[[Be_Natural|Be Natural]]》的[[西裝|西裝]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=108&aid=0002347647|title=레드벨벳, 'Be Natural' 13일 정오 음원공개|date=2014-10-13|publisher=MT Star News|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413151157/https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=108&aid=0002347647}}</ref>。

