|date=2017-11-27|publisher=The 405|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201040329/https://www.thefourohfive.com/music/review/red-velvet-close-out-a-flawless-year-with-the-aptly-titled-perfect-velvet-151|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/33328/1/red-velvet-k-pop-interview|title=Meet the girl group breaking K-Pop’s rules|date=2016-10-12|publisher=Dazed|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227155326/https://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/33328/1/red-velvet-k-pop-interview}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/red-velvet-really-bad-boy-rbb-interview|title=Sweet? Sexy? K-Pop Group Red Velvet Is Both, And Then Some|date=2018-12-21|publisher=Refinery29|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2018-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181222082057/https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/red-velvet-really-bad-boy-rbb-interview}}</ref>。《IZE》雜誌將該組合評為2017年幫助改變韓國女性「被動形象」的成功女性人物之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.ize.co.kr/view.html?no=2017120500337269208|title=2017년의 여성캐릭터│① 소녀도 꽃도 아닌|date=2017-12-05|publisher=The 405|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206140043/https://m.ize.co.kr/view.html?no=2017120500337269208|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。另外，Red Velvet的音樂多樣性得到了《[[時代雜誌|時代]]》雜誌的認可<ref>{{cite web|url=https://time.com/5124176/best-k-pop-artists/|title=These Are the Best K-Pop Groups You Should Know About|date=2018-02-09|publisher=TIME|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519083921/https://time.com/5124176/best-k-pop-artists/}}</ref>。來自《[[時尚_(Vogue)|時尚]]》雜誌的Janelle Okwodu寫道「這個廣受好評的韓國女團在她們的整個演藝生涯中，以其創新的流行音樂統治了排行榜」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vogue.com/article/red-velvet-queendom-fashion-interview|title=Red Velvet on Revisiting Their Old Looks and How They Define “Queendom”|date=2021-10-08|publisher=Vogue|access-date=2022-05-16|archive-date=2021