2015年，Red Velvet也憑《Ice Cream Cake》在韓國年末頒獎典禮包攬了表演獎項，如「[[甜瓜音樂獎|甜瓜音樂獎]]」、「[[Mnet亞洲音樂大獎|Mnet亞洲音樂大獎]]」、「Simply K-Pop Awards」、「[[Gaon_Chart_K-POP大獎|Gaon Chart K-POP大獎]]」。<ref>{{cite web|title=Check Out The Winners Of The '2015 MelOn Music Awards'!|url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2015/11/check-out-the-winners-of-the-2015-melon-music-awards|website=allkpop|accessdate=2017-01-15|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402012509/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2015/11/check-out-the-winners-of-the-2015-melon-music-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Big Bang, EXO win big at 2015 MAMA |website=The Korea Times |url=http://www.koreatimesus.com/big-bang-exo-win-big-at-2015-mama/ |accessdate=2015-12-10 |date=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2015-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211073432/http://www.koreatimesus.com/big-bang-exo-win-big-at-2015-mama/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Simply K-Pop Best Performance Girl Group Announcement|url=https://twitter.com/_Simplykpop/status/675167114894974976|website=Twitter|publisher=Arirang|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2019-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217173446/https://twitter.com/_Simplykpop/status/675167114894974976|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Kim|first1=Mi-hwa|title=제5회 가온K팝어워드, YG 음원-SM 음반 '초강세'..빅뱅·엑소 5관왕(종합)|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/view/stview.php?no=2016021710321665728|website=Star News|publisher=Star News|accessdate=2016-02-17|archive-date=2016-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804121659/http://star.mt.co.kr/view/stview.php?no=2016021710321665728|dead-url=no}}</ref>年結時，更凴正規一輯《[[The_Red|The Red]]》成為美國告示牌2015年十大最佳KPOP專輯的第七名。<ref name="#2"/>

